{
  "stem": "3964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandparents lived in this house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My great-grandparents lived in that house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were things in that house for over 150 years, which belonged to the family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you're allowed to take a little suitcase.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you take?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, all you can take is clothes and some food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever little food we had, we took along, because we didn't know when and where our next meal was gonna to come from.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Six o'clock next morning came-- same SS man, same policeman, with a truck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --they made us go out of the house-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --with our little suitcase we carried, because they told us not more than you can carry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't have many suitcases.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no reason to have a suitcase.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So some of the things we took were packed in boxes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then they put us on a truck with whatever little packages and suitcases we had; and the tears and stress-- horrendous emotional strain-- not knowing where we-- where we're going.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was a lot of commotion and crying going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you know, when you're 14 years old, you understand it, and you don't understand it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I knew what was happening at the moment, but the significance of it did not enter my mind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sure, we were taken away to be resettled, to work on a farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And sure, we knew how to do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We've been farmers all our lives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well-- [SIGHS] --they put us on this truck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And about four hours later, we arrived in Kassel, which was the large-- was a large city with a large Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
